(n = 4). Tubercle variation in the areas: I-2-8, II-4-6, III-3-6, IV-2-4. Measurements. Dorsal scutum maximum length 11.0-12.0; dorsal scutum maximum width 10.0-11.7; prosoma maximum length 4.5-5.0; prosoma maximum width 6.4-7.2; leg femora: I 7.1-8.4; II 13.8-16.2; III 11.0-12.0; IV 13.0-17.0.
